price on the reputation boost

00:53:52.630 --> 00:53:56.290
that you get from having
these humane policies.

00:53:56.290 --> 00:54:00.291
So it's retention, it's
recruiting, it's reputation.

00:54:00.291 --> 00:54:03.172
All of that, if you
